features: Senershuo Ninja air fryer rack can be used as a dehydration rack. The compact three-layer dehydration rack design is convenient for you to quickly use the Ninja Double Air Fryer to make all kinds of dehydrated fruits or dehydrated beef jerky.

Senershuo air fryer rack is easier than ever to dehydrate fruits and meats, lock in nutrition, and the dishwasher-safe design makes cleaning a breeze. The frame of the entire dehydration rack has been carefully polished, without burrs, it is safe to use and feels excellent.

When using the air fryer rack, place the air fryer basket vertically and slowly push the air fryer basket to prevent food from falling. You can also use it as a grill for an air fryer, for grilling steaks or for steaming.

You can use this Senershuo air fryer grill to grill delicious steaks, and at the same time make corresponding side dishes in another air fryer basket of the air fryer, so that you can quickly enjoy the food.

The stackable design provides great convenience and saves you valuable table space. The dishwasher-safe design makes cleaning a breeze and we offer 3pcs Kitchen Silicone Steamer Mesh Non-Stick Pad by free
